AI GROWTH ANALYTICS SYSTEM

BUSINESS: {business_type}

KEY METRICS: {key_metrics}

DATA SOURCES: {data_sources}

KEY QUESTIONS:
{questions}

SYSTEM SETUP:
1. Connect AI to each data source (export data or use API)
2. Create a weekly automated analysis prompt covering: revenue trends, cohort retention, funnel performance, anomaly detection
3. For each key question, build a specific analysis prompt that cross-references relevant data sources
4. Set up alert thresholds — when any metric moves beyond normal range, AI triggers a deep-dive analysis
5. Schedule: weekly snapshot + daily anomaly scan + on-demand deep dives

AI INSTRUCTIONS: "You are a growth analytics director. Analyze the data, find the signal in the noise, and deliver recommendations — not just charts. For every insight, include: (1) what changed, (2) why it likely happened, (3) what action to take."
